sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Main Thread<br/>(UI Updates)
    participant Entity as Shared Entity
    participant BG1 as Background Task 1
    participant BG2 as Background Task 2

    UI->>Entity: Start processing
    Entity->>BG1: Spawn task (file loading)
    Entity->>BG2: Spawn task (computation)

    Note over UI,Entity: UI stays responsive

    BG1-->>Entity: update(): Progress 25%
    Entity->>UI: cx.notify()

    BG2-->>Entity: update(): Progress 50%
    Entity->>UI: cx.notify()

    BG1-->>Entity: update(): Loading complete
    Entity->>UI: cx.notify()

    BG2-->>Entity: update(): Computation complete
    Entity->>UI: cx.notify()

    Note over UI,Entity: Multiple windows see updates<br/>via shared entity handle
